title: 1994 IGA Classic – Singles
text:
<a href="Zina%20Garrison">Zina Garrison-Jackson</a> was the defending champion but lost in the semifinals to <a href="Brenda%20Schultz-McCarthy">Brenda Schultz</a>.
<a href="Meredith%20McGrath">Meredith McGrath</a> won in the final 7–6, 7–6 against Schultz.
Seeds.
A champion seed is indicated in bold text while text in italics indicates the round in which that seed was eliminated.
